    "description": "《风铃》是一款强调连招及战斗体验的平台动作游戏。游戏内设计了上百种可以自由搭配的武器技能，你可以随心所欲的搭配出自己喜欢的战斗风格。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074560/extras/443afd908088f7068caeabbc5c909d2c.poster.avif?t=1761277874\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074560/extras/443afd908088f7068caeabbc5c909d2c.webm?t=1761277874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074560/extras/443afd908088f7068caeabbc5c909d2c.mp4?t=1761277874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在游戏中你扮演的角色是羲，为了救出被封在冰中的师妹，不停的游走于各大秘境，只为集齐材料并铸造出天下最锋利的武器。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074560/extras/7195a46744542df5d7b5066ddaee566c.poster.avif?t=1761277874\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074560/extras/7195a46744542df5d7b5066ddaee566c.webm?t=1761277874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074560/extras/7195a46744542df5d7b5066ddaee566c.mp4?t=1761277874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>每次进入秘境，都是一次全新的rogue体验。rogue过程中得到的buff、技能，都会在角色离开秘境时，融合到角色的武器上。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074560/extras/f30731080f3f0438b863675e9ce62426.poster.avif?t=1761277874\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074560/extras/f30731080f3f0438b863675e9ce62426.webm?t=1761277874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074560/extras/f30731080f3f0438b863675e9ce62426.mp4?t=1761277874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你可以使用秘境中融合出的强力武器去完成天书秘录上的任务，天书秘录上的任务奖励可以永久提升角色的某项属性。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074560/extras/9dbb7009b53af4a2b53e349496d782e6.poster.avif?t=1761277874\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074560/extras/9dbb7009b53af4a2b53e349496d782e6.webm?t=1761277874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074560/extras/9dbb7009b53af4a2b53e349496d782e6.mp4?t=1761277874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>官方QQ群：820958687",
